    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the use of plastic packaging for fruit and vegetables",
        "additional_details": "Instead, retailers can make fruit and vegetables open to the public, who can put them in paper bags. This change should decrease the amount of plastic waste by a huge amount and so also decrease the amount of waste that goes into the sea and kills animals. By doing this we can help prevent the climate crisis.",
        "background": "By banning the use of plastic packaging for fruit and vegetables we can decrease the amount of waste produced every year. A study in America found that 63 percent of waste was caused by packaging.",
